snippet: Bayern Munich put upstarts RB Leipzig firmly in their place by sweeping to an emphatic 3-0 home win, with all the goals coming in the first half, in a disappointingly one-sided top-of-the-table Bundesliga clash on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich put upstarts RB Leipzig firmly in their place by sweeping to an emphatic 3-0 home win, with all the goals coming in the first half, in a disappointingly one-sided top-of-the-table Bundesliga clash on Wednesday.

headline.main: Bayern Sweep Aside 10-Man Leipzig in Top-Of-The-Table Clash
headline.print_headline: Bayern Sweep Aside 10-Man Leipzig in Top-Of-The-Table Clash
